Date et POSIX

jFeries <- gsub(
  pattern = "lundi|mardi|mercredi|jeudi|vendredi", 
  replacement = "ouaip", 
  x= jFeries)

  pattern = "samedi|dimanche", 
  replacement = "ohhh", 
  x= jFeries)
